{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_108","type":"agent_message","text":"I found the real bug: `typeReached` gates resource visibility at runtime, not just image size. `ActorSystem$Settings$` is reached too late, after `ConfigFactory` has already tried and failed to load `reference.conf`. I’m moving the condition up to `ActorSystem$` and widening the allowed package set accordingly, then I’ll rerun validation and the target test."}}
